    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/43ea75b4687a604906e9f6fbc70b9602.webp?t=1763693965\" width=608 height=56 /></span>这是一款<strong>第一人称打老鼠</strong>射击游戏。你将扮演一名灭鼠特工队队员，对抗邪恶的老鼠洪灾：用枪，用猫，扫把和大剑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/23e3ac1874a6006d0ca84dd622e9d4ec.poster.avif?t=1763693965\" width=646 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/23e3ac1874a6006d0ca84dd622e9d4ec.webm?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/23e3ac1874a6006d0ca84dd622e9d4ec.mp4?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-如何成为灭鼠专家:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-玩家需要完成一系列硬核灭鼠任务，重建鼠害入侵下的城市。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-角色控制：WASD移动，移动鼠标控制摄像机。E与武器和物品交互。左键射击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-用枪械和猫？射击/打击敌人，获得金币奖励。合理利用环境道具（易爆物，扫把，剑和盾等等）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-拜托你了！灭鼠特工队！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/ef00fe342c084c72848f3ba24bb3797f.poster.avif?t=1763693965\" width=646 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/ef00fe342c084c72848f3ba24bb3797f.webm?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/ef00fe342c084c72848f3ba24bb3797f.mp4?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/88c4c9b1970a479c7ea6cc348e40e566.poster.avif?t=1763693965\" width=608 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/88c4c9b1970a479c7ea6cc348e40e566.webm?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/88c4c9b1970a479c7ea6cc348e40e566.mp4?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/398a0a1b7bfee3b91ecbaec00eeb88f8.poster.avif?t=1763693965\" width=608 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/398a0a1b7bfee3b91ecbaec00eeb88f8.webm?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/398a0a1b7bfee3b91ecbaec00eeb88f8.mp4?t=1763693965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046490/extras/b3b92627c003de15af14f4c02a095f36.webp?t=1763693965\" width=608 height=56 /></span></p>",
